tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Booker's unbelievable behind-the-back dish to Ayton) 2021/02/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Booker's unbelievable behind-the-back dish to Ayton

videos.description: Devin Booker sneaks past defenders and rides the baseline as he finishes with a smooth layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Booker goes for the up-and-under bucket) 2021/02/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Booker goes for the up-and-under bucket

videos.description: Malik Monk misses the 3-pointer, but Jalen McDaniels is right there to get the points for the Hornets.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (McDaniels cleans up the miss with a slam) 2021/02/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: McDaniels cleans up the miss with a slam

videos.description: Bismack Biyombo misses the bucket after LaMelo Ball drops the dime, but Ball still scores the tip-in shot.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LaMelo's awkward pass ends up back to him for the score) 2021/02/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: LaMelo's awkward pass ends up back to him for the score

videos.description: Devin Booker takes advantage of the open court and jams it down, then says some choice words to the Hornets' bench.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Booker T'd up after big slam) 2021/02/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Booker T'd up after big slam

videos.description: Chris Paul sends the leading pass to Devin Booker who slams it down, and Miles Bridges responds with an alley-oop jam of his own.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA-Play (Hornets, Suns trade dunks for the lead) 2021/02/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hornets, Suns trade dunks for the lead

videos.description: Devin Booker quickly knocks down the deep triple off the inbounds pass while getting fouled by Hayward.

videos.headline: Booker drains the much needed contested 3

videos.description: Devin Booker gets the 3-pointer off in time while possibly drawing a foul, but the games goes final and Charlotte wins 124-121.
